32 SUMMARY
3333 This amendment changes the resolve's requirement that the Department of Health and
3344 Human Services issue 2 requests for proposals for pilot programs to develop child assertive
3355 community treatment teams to a requirement that the department issue one request for
3366 applications. The amendment grants authority to the joint standing committee of the
3377 Legislature having jurisdiction over health and human services matters to report out
3388 legislation related to the report submitted by the department on the outcomes and
